{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56f521b0c5","title":"印发中共中央关于支持美共反迫害斗争的宣传通知的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a30eea1511","index":0,"year":1961,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"56f521b0c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"5cc4cbd20f","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陆游（1125-1210），字务观，号放金，山阴（今浙江绍兴）人，南宋爱国诗人。他生在封建统治阶级向外来侵略势力委曲求和的时代，爱国抱负不为时用，晚年退居家乡。他在《咏梅》词中表现出孤芳自赏、凌凉抑郁的调子。本词用陆游原调原题，但情调完全相反，所以说“反其意而用之”。"},{"id":"4a28670b5c","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"驿外，指驿站附近。古代官办的供传递公文的人中途住宿和换马的处所，称驿站。"}],"contents":[{"id":"abf2cf3885","type":"title","text":"下算子·咏梅","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"5cc4cbd20f","type":"paragraph","text":"读陆游脉梅词，反其意而用之","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"4a28670b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"风雨送春归，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"7dbdb3b379","type":"paragraph","text":"飞雪迎春到。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"556bfbc9a5","type":"paragraph","text":"已是悬崖百丈冰，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"a4bd440e1c","type":"paragraph","text":"犹有花枝俏。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"120484a847","type":"paragraph","text":"俏也不争春，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"a6ab395d49","type":"paragraph","text":"只把春来报。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"4830a3e35b","type":"paragraph","text":"待到山花烂漫时，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"f32d989a0d","type":"paragraph","text":"她在丛中笑。附：陆游原词","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"0b72223c52","type":"subtitle","text":"下算子.咏梅","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"b49a509da3","type":"paragraph","text":"驿外三断桥边，","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"f60e9f09b4","type":"paragraph","text":"寂堂开无主。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"a1398f801b","type":"paragraph","text":"已是黄誉独自愁，","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"07bc706b19","type":"paragraph","text":"更著风和雨。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"047a9fea1e","type":"paragraph","text":"无意苦争春，","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"27f14bf99b","type":"paragraph","text":"一任群芳炉。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"45a230be62","type":"paragraph","text":"零落成泥碾作尘，","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"},{"id":"e4ab21cce1","type":"paragraph","text":"只有香如故。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5"}],"page":{"id":"291721b0fd","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"56f521b0c5","start":508,"end":509}}}},"__N_SSG":true}